    "has_children": false,
    "in_trash": false,
    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "There’s a house at the bottom of the hectic hill with a beautiful vegetable garden out front, and a small older woman comes out the door. Josie recognizes her and immediately walks over to chat. We watch as the lady slowly shows signs of recognition, culminating in excited chatter and an insistence that we took some of the strawberries from her garden. Josie is thrilled and overwhelmed. The woman had said she remembered the three little blonde girls from the house on the hill, as well as the kindness of Josie’s parents. ",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
            "bold": false,
            "italic": false,
            "strikethrough": false,
            "underline": false,
            "code": false,
            "color": "default"
          },
          "plain_text": "There’s a house at the bottom of the hectic hill with a beautiful vegetable garden out front, and a small older woman comes out the door. Josie recognizes her and immediately walks over to chat. We watch as the lady slowly shows signs of recognition, culminating in excited chatter and an insistence that we took some of the strawberries from her garden. Josie is thrilled and overwhelmed. The woman had said she remembered the three little blonde girls from the house on the hill, as well as the kindness of Josie’s parents. ",
